{
  "texts": [
    "Teacher-Student knowledge distillation.",
    "Liang et al. (2023b) utilized GPT-3 to coach a more efficient MWP solver (RoBERTa-based encoderdecoder (Liu et al., 2019)).",
    "They shifted the focus from explaining existing exercises to identifying the student model's learning needs and generating new, tailored exercises.",
    "The resulting smaller LLM achieves competitive accuracy on the SVAMP dataset with significantly fewer parameters compared to state-of-the-art LLMs.",
    "Finetuning on many datasets."
  ]
}